    <string-array name="game_results_tips">
        <item>
            make sequences of more than 2 fast answers (faster than 3 sec.) to multiply the round
            score by 2.
        </item>
        <item>
            a flawless game (one without a single wrong answer) multiplies your overall
            score by 1.5. Don\'t rush, play clean!
        </item>
        <item>
            make use of the time while the metronome is ticking to quickly scan through answers so
            you can guess faster.
        </item>
        <item>
            answering within first 3, 5 or 10 sec. gives you extra points, however for each wrong
            answer you will get twice as less score in the current round.
        </item>
        <item>
            if you want to exclude specific song or directory from the game, you can do so in the
            playlist screen.
        </item>
        <item>
            British scientists have established that clicking "Rate" or "Share" button on the menu
            screen instantly earns you some karma points :)
        </item>
    </string-array>

